					20 More Prayers to Pray as We Approach the Pandemic’s Peak
					
				</h2><div class="deck spacer-top-20 spacer-bottom-15" itemprop="description">Petitioning God is still the most powerful way to respond in crisis.</div>
<div class="article-byline "><span itemprop="author">Jen Pollock Michel</span><span class="pipe"></span><span class="postdate" itemprop="datePublished">April 15, 2020</span></div>
<h2 class="title spacer-top-10"><span class="lang-switcher"><a href="/ct/2020/april-web-only/oraciones-pandemia-covid-19-coronavirus-orar-20-mas-latin.html" class="">
								Espa&ntilde;ol
							</a></span><span class="lang-switcher"><a href="/ct/2020/april-web-only/prayers-for-pandemic-covid-19-coronavirus-20-more-korean.html" class="">
