							</a></span><span class="lang-switcher"><a href="/ct/2020/april-web-only/oracoes-pandemia-orar-covid-19-coronavirus-brasil-20-mais.html" class="">
								Portugu&ecirc;s
							</a></span><span class="lang-switcher"><a href="/ct/2020/april-web-only/prayers-pandemic-covid-19-coronavirus-20-more-chinese-simpl.html" class="">
