								繁体中文
							</a></span><span class="lang-switcher"><a href="/ct/2020/april-web-only/doa-pandemi-covid-19-virus-corona-20-indonesia-bahasa.html" class="">
								Indonesian
							</a></span></h2></div>
</div>
</div>
