									한국어
								</a></span><span class="btn-espanol spacer-right-20 spacer-top-10"><a class="lang-switcher" href="/ct/2020/april-web-only/20-oracoes-pelo-covid-19-coronavirus-orar-pandemia-brasil.html">
									Portugu&ecirc;s
								</a></span><span class="btn-espanol spacer-right-20 spacer-top-10"><a class="lang-switcher" href="/ct/2020/april-web-only/20-prayers-covid-19-coronavirus-pray-pandemic-chinese-simpl.html">
									简体中文
								</a></span><span class="btn-espanol spacer-right-20 spacer-top-10"><a class="lang-switcher" href="/ct/2020/april-web-only/20-prayers-covid-19-coronavirus-pray-pandemic-chinese-trad.html">
